data.description: Beautiful home in the Hammocks with all of the extras storage you will need. Upon entering the home you will be greeted with an open floor plan. The kitchen boasts custom cabinets, granite countertops, stone backsplash, moveable island and wine cooler nook! The office space could be used as a play or entertainment space. Large primary bedroom w/bath with garden tub. French doors from livingroom lead you to heated and cooled screened porch along with an extra covered open area perfect for your outdoor kitchen, and open patio area to swing. The fully fenced back yard also includes a cooled 16x24 workshop, 8x10 lawn tool and equipment storage. Exterior of the home is complete with gutters. Take advantage of all of these amenities in the Cecilia School district. Don't let this one get away
